eally want to do the apartment thing, and I was just like, 'Well, why do not you come and live with me and Josephus just for a little while?\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2588, \"end\": 2596, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josephus\", \"score\": 0.9981825138806306, \"rank\": 0.001820795210869944, \"text\": \"Josephus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josephus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Josephus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the apartment thing\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"a little while\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have an extra room.'\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an extra room\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And he was like, 'oh yeah!'\", \"from\": 2647, \"to\": 2675, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So he was living with us.\", \"from\": 2676, \"to\": 2701, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2698, \"to\": 2700}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I learned a lot about Matt in that one year.\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2746, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2712, \"to\": 2717}, {\"ngram\": \"Matt\", \"from\": 2724, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"that one year\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2745}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I learned that he does not like to wipe off his feet before he leaves the bathroom, so the carpet from the bathroom from his room is always going to be wet and he loves to cut it very, very close when leaving for practice.\", \"from\": 2747, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his feet\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2799}, {\"ngram\": \"the bathroom\", \"from\": 2817, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"the carpet\", \"from\": 2834, \"to\": 2844}, {\"ngram\": \"the bathroom\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"his room\", \"from\": 2868, \"to\": 2876}, {\"ngram\": \"practice\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 2968}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I also learned that at the end of the day he is just a goofy guy, he just likes to have fun.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the end\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3013}, {\"ngram\": \"just a goofy guy\", \"from\": 3020, \"to\": 3036}, {\"ngram\": \"fun\", \"from\": 3060, \"to\": 3063}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He's carefree.\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I remember his favourite saying, 'it is what it is', and I would always be like, 'what the heck does that mean, Matt?'\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3198, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his favourite saying\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3111}, {\"ngram\": \"the heck\", \"from\": 3167, \"to\": 3175}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am carefree but not to the point where I do not have any type of plan, and sometimes he'd just go out for hours.\", \"from\": 3200, \"to\": 3315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 3226, \"to\": 3235}, {\"ngram\": \"any type\", \"from\": 3256, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"plan\", \"from\": 3268, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 3309, \"to\": 3314}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd be like, 'Where have you been?'\", \"from\": 3316, \"to\": 3351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"and he'd go, 'Oh!\", \"from\": 3352, \"to\": 3369, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just walking around.'\\\"\", \"from\": 3370, \"to\": 3397, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hudson-Smith lived with the sprinting Lyles brothers for a year, growing so close that, by a certain point, remembers the Briton, \\\"I was called the third Lyles.\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3437,